{"title":"诗传单","authors":["井岩盾","芮虹灼","燕凌"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":7,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗传单"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一场险恶的战斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井岩盾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一场险恶的战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发生在我们歌唱的时候！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在明媚的阳光里激烈进行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在未来的目标上决定胜负！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一场险恶的战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发生在我们歌唱的时候！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热情的战士们站起来啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国向你们殷切唤呼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它不能把命运交给右派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能陷入卖国的阴谋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党的领导不能动摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换来这教训是无数人头！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捉狐妖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕凌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翘呀翘，翘呀翘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尾巴翘得八丈高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翘到空中摇呀摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狐臭散得满城臊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闻到狐臭心里恼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起钢叉和铁镐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都来捉狐妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切莫叫它溜掉了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夹呀夹，夹呀夹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狐狸夹起烂尾巴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我本无心放毒气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不过尾巴发痒啦！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捶胸顿足号啕哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因臭毛被人拔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等你心软手放松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它又回窝去磨牙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捉呀捉，捉呀捉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许狐妖回老窝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要它改邪来归正，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此不许再撒泼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动物园里养着它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给它吃来给它喝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人学会认狐狸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看它尾巴怎样拖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右派肖像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芮虹灼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我帮助你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你先放下武器"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我帮助你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把两眼紧闭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我帮助你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把双手缚牢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我抽出白刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——帮助你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（北京大学诗刊“红楼”）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}